Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Wedding!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh-ragons, assemble.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.07,0:00:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this is the first time\Nall of us have gotten together.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense for the last installment.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I guess this {\i1}is{\i0} the last one.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's end this with a bang!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(26,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Pure White Dress!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the groom?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.63,0:00:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never allow anyone else \Nto marry Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.46,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down. This is just a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the bride.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.81,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kobayashi? \NIt suits me, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "veil" isn't veiling your horn.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(29,362,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Sacrifice!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.70,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a wedding?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the land where I used to live,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it was customary to offer \Na human heart as tribute during ceremonies.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems terrifying.\NWhy don't we offer something else?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.76,0:01:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.05,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, a little bloodletting bonus, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(25,359,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Matryoshka.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.27,0:01:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A matryoshka?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Spasiba.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? I want to take her home...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.82,0:01:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Marry me.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.86,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill that out.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.03,0:01:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very businesslike.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\t(21,355,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Wedding Aisle.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good way to end things.{whatever, man}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi, what do you think?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, the vows.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take each other in sickness and in health,{intentionally wrong punctuation for surprise factor}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when lounging under the kotatsu,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and when gods descend upon the earth,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and when this world is brought to an end,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I vow that we will keep on loving each other!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.15,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi vows it, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't vow for me!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, the ring exchange...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! That thing is definitely cursed!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It can never be removed, that's all.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you may kiss.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissing is such a bother.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move right on to the honeymoon night!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.33,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\iclip(m 278 1080 b 365 1028 442 1004 525 971 b 511 892 607 854 629 936 b 817 881 1130 864 1334 932 b 1352 899 1363 891 1405 891 b 1442 892 1459 906 1477 932 b 1487 949 1491 966 1487 986 b 1549 1011 1598 1041 1652 1080)}Let's move right on to the honeymoon night!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1272,1564,\c&H000000&)}Just stop!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.80,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that marks the end of the \N{\i1}Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Something{\i0} extras.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We really went off the rails, didn't we?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And to those of you who sat through them with us...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Comment: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.72,Signs,Not important,0,0,0,,"Salami snacks"